{"id":298310,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-拆迁流氓夜闯田书华住宅，南通维权人士/","date":"2013-06-10T02:05:53Z","modified":"2013-06-10T02:05:53Z","title":"维权网 | 拆迁流氓夜闯田书华住宅，南通维权人士去营救被打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日晚</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点半许，江苏如皋田书华向外发出求救信息：一伙自称拆迁公司的，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>多人，闯进她家，强迫她签订拆迁安置协议。此后，田书华的手机就打不通了。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>南通王燕飞，高平、朱磊、高凡菲、如皋储开宏和海安刘强等六人闻讯前去声援田书华。王燕飞等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>人到如皋迎春派出所去报案，寻求保护公民的人身和财产不受侵害，但该所民警置之不理。就在他们离开派出所途中，王燕飞等还没有进田书华家门就被这伙拆迁流氓围殴。这伙拆迁流氓出手狠毒，将王燕飞的牙齿打落。随后，张亮的鼻子也被暴徒打出血。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>现在，张亮等正在南通公安局继续报警，控告如皋市公安局不作为，纵容拆迁暴徒行凶施暴。徐丽艳夫妇和冯兰美也前去声援。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，当田书华发现如皋拆迁流氓闯入其住宅时，也向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，民警到达现场并不制止拆迁流氓的逼签行为，而这伙拆迁流氓竟然有恃无恐，当着警察的面，抢走了田书华的手机。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-u0HEoKIpWDE/UbUx1_tVoOI/AAAAAAAAjLM/xZ46jbFdxpc/s1600/63e12eca-5316-4704-830f-c3394c906b84.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-u0HEoKIpWDE/UbUx1_tVoOI/AAAAAAAAjLM/xZ46jbFdxpc/s320/63e12eca-5316-4704-830f-c3394c906b84.jpg\" width=\"191\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5TaWJOLtoWk/UbUx3VaSFzI/AAAAAAAAjLU/Bc7ZbnEiM4M/s1600/77759a3f-3970-4ddb-b2af-dcc86c3c6363.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5TaWJOLtoWk/UbUx3VaSFzI/AAAAAAAAjLU/Bc7ZbnEiM4M/s320/77759a3f-3970-4ddb-b2af-dcc86c3c6363.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hZOKaklyQm4/UbUx49WoKvI/AAAAAAAAjLc/fj9qCa52A2s/s1600/8372561f-813d-418d-9488-dfacf67c7103.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"191\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hZOKaklyQm4/UbUx49WoKvI/AAAAAAAAjLc/fj9qCa52A2s/s320/8372561f-813d-418d-9488-dfacf67c7103.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}